\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ appeals to me, because neither in Scripture nor in the Mishnah do we find \lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ שאר\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  being used as an 
