\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ Mishnah (Sanh. 8b), And others liable to death - outside of those delineated. But in the expression 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ for which \lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ אחר\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  is used, \lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ שאר\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  is not used. \lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ and you shall beware of your spirit, that it shall not deal 
